						<p>Pillar in the <hi rend="italic">kalyāṇamaṇḍapa</hi> of the Viṭṭhalēśvarasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>1260 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated Śaka 1182, Raudri, Pushya, ba. 10, <hi rend="italic">Makara-sankrānti.</hi> Wednesday, corresponding to 1260 A.D. December 10.</p>						

						<p>Incomplete. It mentions the name of the god Bhōgīśvaradēva.</p>						

